Original Code Source: Dmitry Zavalishion, dz@dz.ru
Description:  
	Phantom Virtual Machine
	Bytecode interpreter and virtual machine services

	NB! With the exception of Windows-based adapter sources,
	this is Phantom KERNEL code. It is run in kernel environment,
	and no usual Unix/Windows system calls are permitted, exept
	for those existing in the Phantom kernel as well (printf is
	a good example).
